JavaScript Udacity Project: Pixel Artmaker

Requirements for this Udacity project: 
- user can create a canvas of individual size
- user can choose a color and color the pixels in the grids
- option to reset the grid to original state
- Udacity provided a CSS and HTML file
- This JavaScript needs to make use of them
- Code should be properly formattted and commented
- code runs errorfree

Instructions: 
Add an integer number for hight and width and choose a color. Then you are ready to color the pixels.  